   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1892_AS_RBH_1_00032"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr Richard
                     Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb730" type="place">III. Seidlgasse 30</rs></hi>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1892_AS_RBH_1_00034"/><salute>Lieber Richard.</salute> Morgen nichts. Eventuell ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c> ich um <time>7</time> ins <rs ref="#pmb34" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Griensteidl</hi></rs>. Gewi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s um <time>10</time>. – Auch <date>So<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>tag</date> wird<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ich nichts machen la<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en, weil da <rs ref="#pmb11491" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Goldschmidt</hi></rs> i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t <pb facs="1892_AS_RBH_1_00035"/>u ich Abend eingeladen bin. Ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chrieb
               eben an <rs ref="#pmb11740" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Loris</hi></rs> wegen eines Wochenabends, eventuell <date>Sam<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date></p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr<lb/><signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
